node.text: Most of our courses for the remainder of 2021 are now full. We will be releasing the 2022 schedule in about October. We will be @smokymountainknifeworks in October for Dealer weekend doing some talks and demos if you don’t get a chance to get to the school this year, come see us for that event. #training #survival #bushcraft #offroad #overlanding #camping #hiking #communicationskills #selfreliance #staydirty #davecanterbury

node.text: Checking fit up and compatibility of a couple prototypes we have in the pipeline. node.text: This is a shot of a recent raised bed made for video by @corporalscorner, if you are not subscribed to his YT channel you are missing some great content using simple tools to do some nice builds. node.text: A chuckbox can take on many forms, this small kit covers everything I need for camp cooking on the road. node.text: The removable trays in the front of the @deckedusa system allow storage of small and quick access items to make truck organizations much less of a chore, with everything contained and easy to get at when needed it has become one of the favorite pieces of my Gladiator build! #jeeplife #offroad #getoutside #davecanterbury
